name: The Practise of Love
description:
Production by Capitol K.
Art by Chris Bianchi.

Harp on The Practise of Love by Serafina Steer.
Mastering by Jac Beloeil.

Words adapted from Errico Malatesta.

Instruments: Dr220, Korg Micro Preset, Nord Lead, SPD20, Roland 201, Freebass, Lexicon PCM60 & Lyon and Healy Harp.
